summary: Get a hint at what\'s inside a container before opening it.
descriptionHtml:
If you like browsing containers, but got sick of opening so many just to find junk, this is for you.
Vanilla game notably distinguishes Fish and Mead Barrels, but there actually are few more types.

-----------------------------------------------------------
Name Changes:

Barrel -> Food Barrel
Barrel -> Ingredient Barrel
Barrel -> Meat Barrel
Barrel -> Potion Barrel
Honningbrew Mead Barrel [Empty] -> Barrel [Empty]

Sack -> Food Sack
Small Sack -> Food Sack
Large Sack -> Food Sack
-----------------------------------------------------------

Always test mods before overwriting your savefile!
author: DSR
